departurePoint.commonName: King's Cross St. Pancras Underground Station

disruptions.description: Your safety is important to us so when carrying large or multiple items of luggage please use lifts where available, should you wish to use the escalators please ensure your luggage is secure on a step and you hold onto both your luggage and the hand rail at all times
Queues are likely at busy times when changing between the Victoria line and District/Circle line platforms due to reconstruction works.
disruptions.additionalInfo: If you are travelling at peak times, or with children or luggage, or have mobility impairment, you will find it easier to change between lines using one of the alternative routes listed on the Victoria information Page. If you travel via Green Park and Westminster, there are lifts available between platforms.
